表格QC表单的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('QC_Table')
and type = 'U')
drop table QC_Table
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: QC_Table */
/*==============================================================*/
create table QC_Table (
ID int identity(1,1),
WorkOrderNo varchar(50) null,
ProductNo varchar(50) null,
ProductDesc varchar(400) null,
DispatchNo varchar(20) not null,
MachineNo varchar(20) not null,
MouldNo varchar(20) not null,
TotalQty int null,
GoodQty AS ([TotalQty]-[BadQty]),
BadQty int null constraint DF__QC_Table__BadQty__625A9A57 default (0),
ProductDate datetime null,
Worker varchar(12) null,
Checker varchar(12) null,
CheckDate datetime not null constraint DF__QC_Table__CheckD__681373AD default getdate(),
Memo varchar(200) null,
constraint PK_QC_Table_1 primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
